{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.280", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.520", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben es geh\u00f6rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seit 2003 geh\u00f6rt die Region Darfur zu den schlimmsten Krisenherden der Welt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.640", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Konflikt im Sudan kostete seither bis zu 600\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Zahlen sind ungenau\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Leben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.920", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2,7\u00a0Millionen Menschen sind innerhalb des Landes auf der Flucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.520", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2,1\u00a0Millionen Menschen sind auf humanit\u00e4re Hilfe angewiesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine traurige und bedr\u00fcckende Bilanz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Gauland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es hat mich erschreckt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie im Zusammenhang mit Afghanistan so wenig gew\u00fcrdigt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.680", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Fortschritte die Bundeswehr in diesem Land erzielt und welche Hilfe sie dort geleistet hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.720", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir UNAMID brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um genau diese Hilfe und Flankierung zu organisieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.360", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darfur ist ein zentraler Brennpunkt in Afrika, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.040", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schl\u00fcsseltransitland und Zufluchtsland f\u00fcr Fl\u00fcchtlinge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mord, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entf\u00fchrung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vergewaltigung und Hungersnot geh\u00f6ren zu den traurigen Wahrheiten dieses Konflikts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tatenlos zuzusehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.640", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Menschenrechte mit F\u00fc\u00dfen getreten werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.960", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen verhungern und aus ihrer Heimat vertrieben werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann keine Option f\u00fcr die internationale Gemeinschaft sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.280", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sigmar Gabriel hatte recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.840", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als er sagte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Freiheit und Recht anderer sind genauso wichtig wie Freiheit und Recht in unserem Land."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In jeder Krise, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in jedem Konflikt m\u00fcssen zun\u00e4chst nat\u00fcrlich diplomatische und politische L\u00f6sungen gesucht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.040", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das soll UNAMID flankieren und leisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.480", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit wenigen Soldaten unterst\u00fctzen wir die Afrikanische Union in ihrem Bestreben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.360", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frieden in dieser Krisenregion zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.120", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "UNAMID steht f\u00fcr ein politisches, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.880", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sicherheitspolitisches, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.280", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "humanit\u00e4res und menschenrechtliches Engagement. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau dieser ganzheitliche Ansatz ist so wichtig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn es darum geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.320", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fluchtursachen zu bek\u00e4mpfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.760", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss man bereit sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.480", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor Ort zu helfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "UNAMID verbessert die humanit\u00e4re Lage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir leisten wichtige Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr Friedensverhandlungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.880", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben Schutzzonen f\u00fcr die Zivilbev\u00f6lkerung eingerichtet und unterst\u00fctzen zum Beispiel auch ein Vorhaben in der beruflichen Bildung im Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Aufgabe liegt in der Wahrnehmung von F\u00fchrungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.040", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Beratungsaufgaben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.360", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem helfen wir bei der Ausbildung und Ausr\u00fcstung truppenstellender Nationen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese verschiedenen Hilfs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Unterst\u00fctzungsma\u00dfnahmen kann niemand ernsthaft ablehnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade jetzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.600", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der augenblicklichen Situation unseres Landes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind Verl\u00e4sslichkeit und Berechenbarkeit in der Au\u00dfen- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.080", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Sicherheitspolitik sehr wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.720", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade weil wir so viele Krisen in der Welt erleben und bearbeiten m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade in der jetzigen Situation w\u00e4re es ein fatales Zeichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.920", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir uns aus internationalen Verpflichtungen zur\u00fcckziehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.480", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen verl\u00e4sslich und berechenbar sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir m\u00fcssen f\u00fcr Kontinuit\u00e4t stehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine positive Entwicklung der Bedrohungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.200", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Sicherheitslage ist erkennbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch sind wir noch lange nicht am Ziel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum ist es wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir die Menschen in diesem Land nicht alleinlassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.760", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich komme zum Ende, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.640", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.120", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Redezeit ist abgelaufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.080", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir die Hoffnung verlieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Situation im Sudan verbessern zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.200", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was sollen dann die Menschen vor Ort sagen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Engagement ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir auch in anderen Regionen dieser Welt Verantwortung tragen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es reicht nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.080", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.560", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eWenn es uns gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.680", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "reicht uns das\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.200", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern wir gehen hinaus und sorgen auch in anderen Regionen f\u00fcr die Einhaltung der Menschenrechte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.240", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat Dr.\u00a0Andreas Nick f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Bundestagsfraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
